cat << EOF
Thoggen is a DVD backup utility ('DVD ripper') for Linux, based on GStreamer
and Gtk+, designed to be easy and straight-forward to use.  It encodes any
number of DVD titles into the ogg/theora video format (with ogg/vorbis audio)
and supports picture cropping and picture resizing.
EOF
